@murffyslurtz If you go the liquid IV route you want to buy from the supplier and you get 30% off with the code POTS30 and 5 bucks off for each pack of 32. 

I’ve only recently started tackling the dysautonomia route in September!

These are the cheaper salt pills I use https://t.co/EVJqmdktNm

@murffyslurtz That’s a sign! 

For my dysautonomia my shoulders were tight because my body wouldn’t hold on to enough salt and thus water. 

When I drink things with a lot of salt like either 250mg salt pills or a liquid IV 500 my shoulders loosen up a lot
